OL,3,CMum's stories helping non-verbal
OL,4,Cdaughter understand terminal cancer
OL,6,FThe six-year-old struggles to
OL,7,Fcommunicate, so her parents use
OL,8,Fsymbols to better understand the world
OL,9,Faround her.
OL,11,FNow, with the help of Overgate Hospice
OL,12,Fand Elsie's special school, Kylie and
OL,13,Fher husband Dan are making stories
OL,14,Fusing the symbols to explain her
OL,15,Fmother's cancer journey.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
