OL,3,CMum's stories helping non-verbal
OL,4,Cdaughter understand terminal cancer
OL,6,FKylie said: "Obviously my cancer is
OL,7,Fterminal, so there will be a point in
OL,8,Flife when Elise will lose me. There
OL,9,Fare so many children out there who are
OL,10,Fneurodiverse and they don't have the
OL,11,Fopportunity to be supported in such a
OL,12,Fdisease."
OL,14,FAs Kylie's treatment changes, her
OL,15,Fparents add to the story with the
OL,16,Fsymbols Elsie is already familiar with.
