OL,3,CMum's stories helping non-verbal
OL,4,Cdaughter understand terminal cancer
OL,6,FDan said: "It's reassuring to know
OL,7,Fthat Elsie is being prepared the best
OL,8,Fthat she can be. Hopefully it's years
OL,9,Fdown the line and we don't have to
OL,10,Fthink about the worst that can happen
OL,11,Ffor a long time.
OL,13,F"But to know that there are people
OL,14,Fthere that are helping Elsie, and
OL,15,Fhelping Elise's level of
OL,16,Funderstanding, not only with regard to
OL,17,Fcancer but illness and stuff as well,
OL,18,Fand coming to terms with what she's
OL,19,Fgoing to have to deal with."
