OL,4,Cdaughter understand terminal cancer
OL,6,FLisa Mileszkowska, from Overgate
OL,7,FHospice, said: "The thing that (Kylie)
OL,8,Fsaid to me was that she didn't want
OL,9,FElsie to think that mum had just left
OL,10,Fher.
OL,12,F"I was actually trying to source
OL,13,Fsomething to help Kylie to talk to
OL,14,FElsie about a condition, and there's
OL,15,Fjust very little out there."
OL,17,FNow the family are looking at ways
OL,18,Fthey can use the stories they have
OL,19,Fcreated to help neurodiverse children
OL,20,Fcome to term with life limiting
OL,21,Fillness.
