OL,6,FFamily friend Helen Fitzgerald said:
OL,7,F"It's hard. So hard for children, but
OL,8,Fespecially children with them
OL,9,Fadditional needs to to understand
OL,10,Fwhat's happening and so something in
OL,11,Fplace to just make it a little bit
OL,12,Feasier, I think. And we really need
OL,13,Fit. And it's Kylie's goal and I would
OL,14,Flove her to get that book out."
